Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這 艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾洛克艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾剛蒂亞需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對我過於沉重…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優秀起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到能挺起胸膛向你父親做出交待為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團長！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團長…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已確認地球的位置坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已根據銀河同盟的標準坐標確定當前位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠歸隊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸需要藉助超光速飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 僅憑本機無法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救信號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機緊急迫降到地球後發出的最初信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達銀河同盟大約需要6582年16小時20分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結論 回歸大部隊事實上不具備可操作性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了…
